QuestData.Title: The Reel Deal
QuestData.Description:
<These fishing rods must have been left behind when Art moved from the beach. Most of them seem to have bites.
Maybe you should reel them up and see what's hooked?>
QuestData.LogDescription: Reel in $1oa Fishing Rods in Snapclaw Shore.
QuestData.RewardText:
<That looks like the last of Art's rods.
You manage to salvage some of Art's bait with your catch.
Waste not, want not>
